                'public/css/rxn-theming.css: (a) html/body con overflow-x:clip + max-width:100vw. (b) .rxn-form-shell max-width:100% con override sobre container/container-xl/lg/md/sm. (c) bloque light-mode extendido: acotado por .notas-split, .crm-agenda-shell, .crm-tratativas-shell, .crm-llamadas-shell, .rxn-live-shell — neutraliza bg-dark/text-light/border-secondary. (d) Tablas .table-dark en .rxn-live-shell: override via CSS vars de Bootstrap (--bs-table-bg/color/striped-bg/hover-bg/border-color). (e) Dropdowns .dropdown-menu-dark idem via vars.',
